I was raised as a conservative small town country girl and moved to the city and got a taste of reality. I ran away from home (without telling anyone) after I found out a dark family secret. I had no idea what was going to happen next. Coming to the city, I was able to experience a lot of firsts and get in touch with the side of me that was sheltered away. My experiences are what inspires my music. I've been singing all of my life, and sang in choir in church. I was never able to listen to music on the radio, but now that side of me is history. I think everyone should be in touch with their deeper, darker and sexy side... Which is what I live by now!

Klaas2, a rising star in the world of alternative R&B, has been making waves with his unique blend of soulful melodies and introspective rap lyrics. Born and raised in Poland, this multifaceted artist's journey to Los Santos was anything but ordinary. Enduring a tumultuous divorce that left him with nothing, Klaas2 found solace and inspiration in music, using it as a means to heal and rise above life's challenges. From a young age, Klaas2 showed a natural talent for creating music, experimenting with various instruments and honing his skills as a producer and mixer. Drawing from a wide range of influences, Klaas2's sound is a fresh fusion of R&B, hip-hop, and electronic elements, captivating listeners with his heartfelt stories and catchy hooks. As both a vocalist and a rapper, Klaas2 exhibits a rare versatility that sets him apart from other artists in the genre. Upon arriving in Los Santos, Klaas2 quickly made a name for himself in the local music scene, earning the respect and admiration of his peers. His relentless dedication to his craft, combined with his signature style, caught the attention of our label, and we couldn't be more thrilled to have him as part of our roster. As Klaas2 continues to evolve as an artist, we eagerly anticipate what the future holds for him. His undeniable talent and unwavering passion for music are the driving forces that will undoubtedly propel him to new heights in the industry. We are proud to support Klaas2 on his journey and look forward to sharing his music with the world.

Raiden Rufio is an Australian-born Filipino, musician and songwriter who is currently based in Los Santos. His influences include the Gorillaz, Arctic Monkeys and The Strokes. Rufio's music is a blend of rock and pop and his lyrics often explore themes of love, loss, and self-discovery. Rufio released his debut single, Hellhounds of the Sea in 2022. The single was well-received by critics and fans alike, and it helped to establish Rufio as a rising star in the music industry. Rufio is a passionate and dedicated musician, and he is always looking for new ways to express himself through music.

Sydney, a brave artist, uses her music as a powerful tool for self-expression and empowerment. Drawing from her own experiences with DID and PTSD, she fearlessly addresses mental health and encourages others to embrace their uniqueness. Through soulful indie rock melodies and poignant lyrics, she creates a safe space for vulnerability, urging listeners to break free from societal expectations and speak their truth. Sydney's music serves as a beacon of hope, reminding us that embracing our differences is what truly makes us extraordinary.
